{"tid":2300359,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《The Last of Us Part II》奪金搖桿年度遊戲、最佳劇情","createTime":"2020-11-25T12:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T14:52:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7072647b99285e3373bfa04278d1ba70681926c3","tid":2300359,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"之前同大家報導過，Metacritic玩家評分僅為5.7、一出就被人鬧到爆嘅《The Last of Us Part II》獲得The Game Award 2020嘅10項提名，大家應該都覺得難以接受。但近日《The Last of Us Part II》於標榜係公眾投票嘅英國「The Golden Joystick Award」年度遊戲頒獎禮，竟然都奪得年度遊戲、最佳劇情等大作，真係令我開始懷疑唔通我先係少數？<br />\n<br />\n嗱我Check過架啦，由Gamesradar主辦嘅「Golden Joystick Awards」呢，提名名單就係由多間英國遊戲媒體及記者選出，但最後邊個拎獎，佢哋就話完全係公眾投票嘅結果。換言之，係公眾將《The Last of Us Part II》選為年度遊戲、最佳劇情、最佳視覺設計、最佳音效及Playstation年度遊戲，再加上開發商Naughty Dog奪得年度最佳工作室，20個獎中佢拎咗6個。<br />\n<br />\n特別值得一提嘅係，年度遊戲第二名係被指大量抄襲《薩爾達傳說 曠野之德》、又被指有後門程式嘅中國開發遊戲、再被發現審查「香港」、「台灣」字句嘅《原神》。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Gamesradar"},{"pid":"65e9948db5252d705f4e1aa54dec18972fd3283b","tid":2300359,"uid":52939,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"左膠死全家啦dllmch"},{"pid":"f8db7c6838a262cdb72124d159ccb08c8acdb538","tid":2300359,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65e9948db5252d705f4e1aa54dec18972fd3283b","tid":2300359,"uid":52939,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"左膠死全家啦dllmch"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"寫衰Ellie<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfe0c175263047e9aa33cd75f18a7dbc524b88d","tid":2300359,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"做咩扮印狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202cda66b0ea53223c7fac2c71864a3f5bdb2d61","tid":2300359,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdfe0c175263047e9aa33cd75f18a7dbc524b88d","tid":2300359,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc